---
title: Cal Smart Italian Wedding Soup with Turkey and Parmesan
description: The soup we all know and love has gotten a Cal Smart makeover! All of the classic players are here, with DIY, herbed turkey sausage mix and a deliciously hearty mix of veg and pasta. This is sure to please!

